   Renesas S4 Spider BSP ROM Writer

2022/02/25	Kuninori Morimoto <kuninori.morimoto.gx@renesas.com>
=============================================

-------------------------------
* What is Renesas Spider ?
-------------------------------

	R-Car S4 Reference Board/Spider

		https://www.renesas.com/jp/ja/products/automotive-products/automotive-system-chips-socs/rtp8a779f0askb0sp2s-r-car-s4-reference-boardspider

-------------------------------
* How to get ROM ?
-------------------------------

	Please Contact to [Renesas Sales team] or
	[Renesas appointed store Sales team]

-------------------------------
* premise
-------------------------------

	This ROM Writer is assuming your Spider board
	already setup [SCIF baudrate] as [1843200]
	via [S4 Spider Configuration Tool]

-------------------------------
* Serial connection
-------------------------------

	[Host PC] <--> [Spider CN21] (/dev/ttyUSBx)

-------------------------------
* How to use ?
-------------------------------

	linux/README
	windows/README
